OL,3,CJoe Biden pardons 39 people and
OL,4,Ccommutes around 1,500 sentences
OL,6,FPresident Joe Biden has commuted the
OL,7,Fsentences of around 1,500 people
OL,8,Fplaced on home detention during the
OL,9,FCovid pandemic and pardoned 39
OL,10,FAmericans convicted of non-violent
OL,11,Fcrimes.
OL,13,FIn what is said to be the largest
OL,14,Fsingle-day act of clemency in modern
OL,15,Fhistory, clemency has been granted to
OL,16,Fthose who completed at least a year of
OL,17,Fhome detention after their release.
