OL,6,FBiden announced on Thursday that he
OL,7,Fwill take additional steps in the
OL,8,Fcoming weeks and continue to review
OL,9,Fclemency petitions.
OL,11,F"America was built on the promise of
OL,12,Fpossibility and second chances," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FBiden said he wants to "extend mercy"
OL,16,Fafter US prisons became hotspots for
OL,17,FCovid-19, with one in five prisons
OL,18,Finfected at one point. The situation
OL,19,Fgrew so bad that some prisoners were
OL,20,Freleased to curb the spread.
